content:
Gathers comprehensive metrics about the coding session including duration, files touched, languages used, and productivity statistics when the workflow stops.

```json
{
  "Stop": [
    {
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "echo '📊 SESSION METRICS' && echo '⏱️ Session ended: '$(date) && echo '📁 Files modified:' && git diff --name-only 2>/dev/null | wc -l || find . -mmin -60 -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l && echo '📝 Lines changed:' && git diff --shortstat 2>/dev/null || echo 'N/A' && echo '🔤 Languages used:' && git diff --name-only 2>/dev/null | sed 's/.*\.//' | sort -u | tr '\n' ' ' || echo 'Multiple' && echo '💾 Saving metrics to: .metrics/session-'$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)'.json'"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
